headline.print_headline: France's Dusautoir, Guitoune Out of Six Nations
headline.main: France's Dusautoir, Guitoune Out of Six Nations

lead_paragraph: France captain Thierry Dusautoir and winger Sofiane Guitoune have both been ruled out of the Six Nations championship after sustaining serious injuries in the Heineken Cup this weekend.
